TIME TRAVEL - we can go back in time and read the table data as it was earlier
SELECT * FROM table_name VERSION AS OF 3;
SELECT * FROM table_name TIMESTAMP AS OF "2025-01-01";

with the help of this we can even roll back table to older version
DESC HISTORY table_name; --> to get table version num
RESTORE table_name TO VERSION AS OF 33;

