TYPES OF CLONES
1. SHALLOW CLONE - clone/copy only metadata, here data points to the same table- very fast and cheap
2. DEEP CLONE - copy metadata + actual data -- its actually full data copy
        query -  CREATE TABLE  new_table  SHALLOW CLONE old_table'

